--- head-2010-10-11.orig/drivers/acpi/pci_irq.c	2010-10-11 16:04:25.000000000 +0200
+++ head-2010-10-11/drivers/acpi/pci_irq.c	2010-10-11 11:03:06.000000000 +0200
